    "body" : "<p>If you just need something simple and more of a verification.</p>\n\n<pre><code>public String getKey(String key)\n{\n    if(map.containsKey(key)\n    {\n        return key;\n    }\n    return null;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then you can search for any key.</p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.println( \"Does this key exist? : \" + getKey(\"United\") );\n</code></pre>\n"
