    "answer_id" : 43822015,
    "question_id" : 10462819,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>To get <strong>Key</strong> and its <strong>value</strong>   </p>\n\n<p>e.g</p>\n\n<pre><code>private Map&lt;String, Integer&gt; team1 = new HashMap&lt;String, Integer&gt;();\n  team1.put(\"United\", 5);\n  team1.put(\"Barcelona\", 6);\n    for (String key:team1.keySet()){\n                     System.out.println(\"Key:\" + key +\" Value:\" + team1.get(key)+\" Count:\"+Collections.frequency(team1, key));// Get Key and value and count\n                }\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Will print:</strong> Key: United Value:5 \n                Key: Barcelona Value:6</p>\n"
  }, {
