    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>A solution can be, if you know the key position, convert the keys into an String array and return the value in the position:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public String getKey(int pos, Map map) {\n    String[] keys = (String[]) map.keySet().toArray(new String[0]);\n\n    return keys[pos];\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
