  "title" : "Get keys from HashMap in Java",
  "body" : "<p>I have a Hashmap in Java like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>private Map&lt;String, Integer&gt; team1 = new HashMap&lt;String, Integer&gt;();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then I fill it like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>team1.put(\"United\", 5);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>How can I get the keys?  Something like: <code>team1.getKey()</code> to return \"United\".</p>\n"
